---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
description: Roel van Bergen writes and speaks about software craft, AI, personal growth, and practical Zen.
---

<section class="hero-pond">
  <div id="koi-pond-container" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hero-paper"></div>
  <div class="hero-content relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-16 min-h-[88vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl py-24">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-8">Practical Zen for the augmented age</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        High-performance code.<br>
        <span>Fully human work.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-copy">
        I am Roel van Bergen, a software engineer, coach, speaker, and Zen teacher. I build and explore technology that helps people work with more clarity, trust, and capability without losing craft, attention, or one another.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-10">
        <a href="/blog/" class="button-primary">Enter the writing garden</a>
        <a href="/talks/" class="button-secondary">Explore speaking topics</a>
      </div>
      <p class="interaction-hint">Click or tap the pond to feed the koi.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
  <div class="section-intro">
    <div class="eyebrow">Three connected paths</div>
    <h2>The engine, the inner voice, and the space between.</h2>
    <p>My work lives where engineering practice meets human attention. Software is a human system before it is a technical one, and each shapes how the other can grow.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar-grid mt-12">
    <article class="pillar-card pillar-engineering">
      <span class="pillar-number">01</span>
      <div>
        <p class="pillar-label">Engineering</p>
        <h3>The engine</h3>
        <p>Software craftsmanship, explicit architecture, humane AI collaboration, and the engineering discipline that turns speed into dependable progress.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="pillar-card pillar-coaching">
      <span class="pillar-number">02</span>
      <div>
        <p class="pillar-label">Coaching</p>
        <h3>The inner voice</h3>
        <p>Perfectionism, self-compassion, sustainable performance, and learning to work with the critic rather than beneath it.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="pillar-card pillar-zen">
      <span class="pillar-number">03</span>
      <div>
        <p class="pillar-label">Zen</p>
        <h3>The presence</h3>
        <p>Attention as a practical skill: slowing down enough to see clearly, choose deliberately, and become one with what you do.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="ink-section">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="section-intro section-intro-light">
        <div class="eyebrow">Fresh from the garden</div>
        <h2>Latest writing</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/blog/" class="text-link text-stone-300">View all {{ collections.post | length }} articles</a>
    </div>

    <div class="featured-post-grid">
      {%- for post in collections.post | reverse | head(3) -%}
      <article class="featured-post">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="featured-image">
          <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
        </a>
        <div class="featured-body">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <span>{{ post.data.pillar }}</span>
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </div>
          <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="text-link">Continue reading</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
  <div class="invitation-panel">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow mb-5">Bring the conversation into the room</div>
      <h2>Speaking and workshops for teams navigating speed, craft, and humanity.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>I turn these ideas into practical talks and reflective sessions that help engineering teams build shared clarity, make better decisions, and work together with confidence.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-7">
        <a href="/talks/" class="button-primary">Speaking topics</a>
        <a href="/trainings/" class="button-secondary">How I can help</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="/assets/js/koi-pond.js"></script>
